<![CDATA[<div style="text-align: left;"><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Please do not respond to this email. This email was sent from an unattended mailbox, and replies are not reviewed. Please instead contact your Staffing representative on {!Job_placement__c.Staffing_Associate_email__c}</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Dear {!Job_placement__c.Contact_Name__c},</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Congratulations on being appointed as {!Job_placement__c.Role__c} on NCS with The Challenge on {!Job_placement__c.Wave__c}.</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Your total pay for this part of the role will be {!Job_placement__c.Total_gross_pay__c}, this includes pay for &nbsp;{!Job_placement__c.Annual_Leave_entitlement__c} day(s), "Holiday Period"; per "Wave Contract", which is subject to tax and national insurance deductions.&nbsp;</font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">This payment will cover the following parts of the programme - &nbsp;NCS: Personal Challenge, NCS: Team Challenge and NCS: Real Challenge Design (one or more will be relevant to your role). Payments for NCS: The Real Challenge Action will be communicated to you at a later date once you have completed them.</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</span></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">You will be paid on {!Job_placement__c.Payroll_payment_date__c}. Tax and NI deductions will be made from this payment.&nbsp;</font><font face="arial" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.818181991577148px;">We reserve the right to deduct pay for any&nbsp;</span></font><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">unauthorised</span><font face="arial" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.818181991577148px;">&nbsp;absences</span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">This payment structure has two principles: (a) to ensure that staff members pay the appropriate level of tax in the correct month and (b) to enable staff members to receive payment in reasonable time.</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Yours sincerely,</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">NCS with The Challenge&nbsp;</span></div><div><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">{!Job_placement__c.Staffing_Associate_email__c}</span></div><div><br></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">2.4.1b</font></div></div>]]></td>
